title: "A conjectural cardinality envelope for the condensed classifying anima of spectral infinity-topoi: a synthesis across geometric and analogical instances"
version: "v1.2.2-preprint"
doi: "10.5281/zenodo.20184660"
date-released: "2026-05-14"
authors:
